The '''Starcrash Brigade''' was one of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire's]] elite assault forces. It was responsible for deploying a lethal strain of [[hive virus]] into [[Firrerre/Legends|Firrerre]], which quickly wiped out all life on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]].

